{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "5.080", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau Pr\u00e4sidentin! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "5.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "5.081", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "5.081", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "5.082", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die AfD-Fraktion fordert in dem heute vorliegenden Antrag, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "5.082", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "5.680", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "den Solidarit\u00e4tszuschlag abzuschaffen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "5.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "6.840", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das w\u00fcrde im Bundeshaushalt eine L\u00fccke von 18\u00a0Milliarden Euro rei\u00dfen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "6.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "6.880", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Damit klar ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "6.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "6.881", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wor\u00fcber wir hier sprechen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "6.881", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "6.882", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist ungef\u00e4hr so viel, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "6.882", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "6.883", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie dem Bundesministerium f\u00fcr Bildung und Forschung insgesamt zur Verf\u00fcgung steht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "6.883", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "6.884", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das k\u00f6nnte man dann also einstampfen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "6.884", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "6.885", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist ungef\u00e4hr doppelt so viel wie das, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "6.885", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "6.886", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was im Haushalt des Familienministeriums vorgesehen ist. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "6.886", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "6.887", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wer hier vorschl\u00e4gt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "6.887", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "6.888", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "eine solche L\u00fccke in den Bundeshaushalt zu rei\u00dfen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "6.888", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "6.889", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der muss nat\u00fcrlich auch dazusagen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "6.889", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "6.890", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie er diese L\u00fccke wieder schlie\u00dfen m\u00f6chte."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "6.890", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "6.891", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nun wissen wir von Ihnen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "6.891", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "6.892", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Sie den Spitzensteuersatz nicht erh\u00f6hen wollen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "6.892", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "6.893", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ganz im Gegenteil. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "6.893", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "6.894", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir wissen auch, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "6.894", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "7.400", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Sie die Verm\u00f6gensteuer nicht wieder einf\u00fchren wollen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "7.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "8.560", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie wollen sogar die Erbschaftsteuer abschaffen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "8.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "8.561", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch zu neuen Krediten sind sie nicht bereit. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "8.561", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "8.562", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Also sagen Sie doch einmal, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "8.562", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "8.563", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie Sie diese L\u00fccke schlie\u00dfen wollen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "8.563", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "8.880", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das geh\u00f6rt n\u00e4mlich zur Wahrheit dazu."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "8.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "9.120", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u2013\u00a0Durch Einsparungen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "9.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "9.160", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber in dieser Gr\u00f6\u00dfenordnung haben Sie nicht viele M\u00f6glichkeiten zu Einsparungen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "9.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "9.161", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sagen Sie Ihren W\u00e4hlerinnen und W\u00e4hlern doch bitte, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "9.161", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "9.280", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Sie an die Grundsicherung im Alter heranwollen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "9.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "10.040", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Sie medizinische Leistungen einschr\u00e4nken wollen und dass Sie die Unterst\u00fctzung f\u00fcr Familien zur\u00fcckfahren wollen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "10.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "10.560", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das geh\u00f6rt zur Wahrheit dazu."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "10.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "11.040", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zur Wahrheit geh\u00f6rt im \u00dcbrigen auch\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "11.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "11.360", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das muss man wieder erw\u00e4hnen\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "11.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "11.800", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass der Solidarit\u00e4tszuschlag als allgemeine Steuer nicht an den Aufbau Ost gekoppelt ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "11.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "11.801", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern dass wir mit diesen Einnahmen im Bundeshaushalt auch andere Dinge bezahlen k\u00f6nnen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "11.801", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "11.802", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Entschuldigen Sie, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "11.802", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "11.803", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ich m\u00f6chte Sie fragen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "11.803", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "11.804", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ob Sie eine Zwischenfrage oder -bemerkung von Herrn Glaser zulassen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "11.804", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "12.200", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Kollege hat vorhin schon etwas gefragt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "12.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "12.280", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Gut."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "12.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "12.680", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zur Wahrheit geh\u00f6rt auch, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "12.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.160", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass diese Einnahmen nicht an den Aufbau Ost gekoppelt sind, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.960", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern dass damit auch andere Leistungen bezahlt werden k\u00f6nnen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "15.840", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Damit wird zum Beispiel der Ausbau von Kitapl\u00e4tzen bezahlt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "15.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "16.360", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und zwar in Ost und West. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "16.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "17.080", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Damit k\u00f6nnen wir das Kindergeld bezahlen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "17.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "17.560", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Damit k\u00f6nnen wir das BAf\u00f6G bezahlen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "17.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "18.920", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Damit k\u00f6nnen wir zum Beispiel Ma\u00dfnahmen gegen Altersarmut bezahlen und im \u00dcbrigen auch Programme gegen Rechtsextremismus. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "18.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "19.080", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "N\u00f6tig haben wir das."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "19.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "19.520", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wahr ist im \u00dcbrigen auch, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "19.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "19.680", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "19.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "19.840", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "oftmals ist das nicht bekannt\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "19.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "20.800", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nicht blo\u00df Westdeutsche den Solidarit\u00e4tszuschlag bezahlen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "20.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "21.000", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern nat\u00fcrlich auch Ostdeutsche."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "21.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "21.001", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Grenze verl\u00e4uft eben nicht zwischen West und Ost, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "21.001", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "21.002", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern die Grenze verl\u00e4uft zwischen denjenigen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "21.002", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "21.003", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die mehr Einkommen haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "21.003", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "21.004", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und denjenigen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "21.004", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "21.005", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die weniger Einkommen haben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "21.005", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "21.006", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist doch der entscheidende Unterschied."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "21.006", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "21.007", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Da muss man einmal ganz klar sagen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "21.007", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "21.008", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was Sie machen wollen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "21.008", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "21.009", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ein Bundestagsabgeordneter, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "21.009", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "21.010", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "also wir alle, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "21.010", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "21.011", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zahlt im Monat durchschnittlich 130\u00a0Euro f\u00fcr den Solidarit\u00e4tszuschlag, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "21.011", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "21.012", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "je nachdem, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "21.012", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "21.013", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie viel Kinder er hat. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "21.013", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "21.014", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "130\u00a0Euro bei einem Einkommen von 10\u00a0000\u00a0Euro brutto: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "21.014", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "21.015", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mir kommen die Tr\u00e4nen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "21.015", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "21.016", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Eine Familie mit zwei Kindern, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "21.016", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "21.017", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die maximal 4\u00a0400\u00a0Euro brutto im Monat zur Verf\u00fcgung hat\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "21.017", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "21.018", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "also alle, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "21.018", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "21.019", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die weniger haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "21.019", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "21.020", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "fallen auch darunter\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "21.020", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "21.021", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "bezahlt \u00fcberhaupt keinen Solidarit\u00e4tszuschlag. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "21.021", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "21.022", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Jetzt m\u00f6chte ich einmal sehen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "21.022", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "21.023", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie Sie diesen Familien erkl\u00e4ren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "21.023", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "21.024", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wem hier etwas genommen und wem etwas gegeben werden soll. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "21.024", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "21.800", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Diese Familien sind n\u00e4mlich auf staatliche Unterst\u00fctzungsleistungen angewiesen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "21.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "22.960", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn man das so betrachtet, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "22.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "26.760", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass n\u00e4mlich der Solidarit\u00e4tszuschlag von denen bezahlt wird, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "26.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "27.440", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die mehr haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "27.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "27.441", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "w\u00e4hrend diejenigen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "27.441", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "27.442", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die weniger haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "27.442", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "27.800", 
   "id": "s000086", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nichts bezahlen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "27.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "28.000", 
   "id": "s000087", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann bekommt der Begriff \u201eSolidarit\u00e4tszuschlag\u201c eine ganz neue Bedeutung."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "28.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "28.240", 
   "id": "s000088", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In diesem Sinne brauchen wir die Solidarit\u00e4t in unserer Gesellschaft dringender denn je. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "28.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "29.600", 
